Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.54,0:01:34.73,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,yoake ga osokute jirettai
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.75,0:01:34.73,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,One, two, Sunshine four...WE GO!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.75,0:01:39.86,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,ichi, ni, Sunshine yon...we go!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.88,0:01:39.86,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,We...made it this far
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.88,0:01:45.87,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,ore tachi wa...koko made kitaze
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.89,0:01:45.87,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,We go...to where the dream is
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.89,0:01:48.74,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,ore tachi wa iku...yume no arika e
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.76,0:01:48.74,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,We won’t left anyone behind
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.76,0:01:53.83,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,dare mo oitekanaize--
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.85,0:01:53.83,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,Keep going forward, that’s our pledge
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.85,0:01:56.46,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,nshin aru nomi sore ga chikai
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.48,0:01:56.46,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,Since the day that the dream began
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.48,0:02:00.55,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,yume ga hajimatta ano hi kara
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.57,0:02:00.55,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,the future that I’m \Naiming at hasn’t changed
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.57,0:02:04.68,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,mezasu mirai wa onaji--
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.70,0:02:04.68,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,I can’t stand still, I can’t stop
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.70,0:02:07.30,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,tto dekinai tomarenai
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.32,0:02:07.30,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,The sun of my heart will never set
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.32,0:02:11.56,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,kokoro no taiyou shizumanai
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.58,0:02:11.56,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,One, two, Sunshine
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.58,0:02:15.73,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,ichi, ni, Sunshine
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.75,0:02:15.73,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,One, two, Sunshine
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.75,0:02:19.69,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,ichi, ni, Sunshine
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.71,0:02:19.69,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,One, two, Sunshine four...WE GO!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.71,0:02:27.71,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,ichi, ni, Sunshine yon...we go!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.30,0:02:35.08,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,WE GO!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.10,0:02:38.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All the pirates who are \Nafter the One Piece...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.73,0:02:45.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...head for the New World, the \Nsecond half of the Grand Line.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.76,0:02:49.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,However, no one has ever fully explored it
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.32,0:02:53.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,except for Gold Roger, King of the Pirates.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.42,0:03:00.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The New World has ruined many \Npirates' dreams and ambitions.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.47,0:03:02.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, Monkey D. Luffy,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.34,0:03:06.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,a boy whose body turned to rubber \Nafter he ate the Gum-Gum Fruit,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.67,0:03:08.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and his friends venture into that sea.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.01,0:03:15.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna become the King of the Pirates!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.33,0:03:17.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,After surviving a fierce battle,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.74,0:03:20.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the Straw Hats finally \Nentered the New World,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.79,0:03:23.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the harshest sea ruled by the Four Emperors.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.73,0:03:27.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,After receiving an emergency signal, \Nthey landed on Punk Hazard Island.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.78,0:03:31.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was a strange island \Ndivided into two parts;
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.37,0:03:33.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the Burning Lands and the Ice Lands.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.83,0:03:41.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sink to your death, Devil Fruit eaters!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.58,0:03:47.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Cut that crap. Let us see \Ninside the laboratory.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.09,0:03:49.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm the only one here!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.49,0:03:53.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If Straw Hat comes, I'll \Nchop his head off for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.71,0:04:01.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If that's all you have to say, go home!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.54,0:04:06.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I made it out!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.99,0:04:09.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,One, two, three...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.61,0:04:13.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Super!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.79,0:04:16.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Straw Hats?! Children?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.56,0:04:20.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I got out of the building! I can go home!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.98,0:04:22.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, you're...!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.92,0:04:26.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was wondering who this \Nvillainous guy was! Smoker!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.60,0:04:29.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And you, cutie!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.22,0:04:32.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is not good! The Navy's here!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.08,0:04:34.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We can't escape from here! \NLet's look for another exit!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.76,0:04:36.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Get inside!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.93,0:04:39.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What brought the Navy to such a place?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.70,0:04:41.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know! Just run!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.92,0:04:44.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry up, kids! Go to the back!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.90,0:04:47.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There should be a backdoor!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.06,0:04:49.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everybody, let's catch the Straw Hats!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.63,0:04:51.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Room.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.70,0:04:58.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Takt!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.16,0:05:06.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.71,0:05:22.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"In a Real Pinch! Luffy Sinks \Ninto the Ice-cold Lake!"
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.07,0:05:31.53,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,PUNK HAZARD ISLAND - THE \NMIDDLE LAKE LUFFY'S GROUP
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.55,0:05:39.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fire!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.88,0:05:49.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Aim at the bottom of the boat!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.34,0:05:51.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go back!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.23,0:05:55.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What're you talking about, Usopp?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.19,0:05:57.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Advance!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.23,0:06:02.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You have no idea what's going on, do you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.61,0:06:08.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're trying to make us fall into the lake!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.52,0:06:13.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can't get away from me - Brownbeard-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.46,0:06:16.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who are you, again?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.49,0:06:18.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't tell me you don't know who I am!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.45,0:06:24.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm a former pirate with an 80 \Nmillion 60 thousand berry bounty!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.21,0:06:27.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Brownbeard-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.42,0:06:30.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Brownbeard-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.96,0:06:38.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Brownbeard-sama! Sama... \NSama... Sama... Sama...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.01,0:06:51.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We've never heard of you!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.41,0:06:59.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How can they be so ignorant?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.32,0:07:07.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Take this! An angry shot!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.13,0:07:08.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn, those bastards!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.67,0:07:11.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're gonna fall!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.73,0:07:15.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh no!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.97,0:07:19.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Yes! He did it!\N--That's our Boss!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.89,0:07:26.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The boat capsized!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.42,0:07:29.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How's that?! Struggle as much as you like
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.76,0:07:37.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but you'll be swallowed by the water!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.70,0:07:43.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's cold!!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.21,0:07:50.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My body's gonna turn to ice \Nin a matter of minutes!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.01,0:07:52.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dammit!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.12,0:07:55.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm losing my strength...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.02,0:07:59.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You could've fought back, Duffy!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.45,0:08:04.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bud you didn't shtop recruiting zem!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.22,0:08:07.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh no! My mouth is freebing...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.83,0:08:10.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Zorry. I give up.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.21,0:08:12.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't need zem to join our crew.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.56,0:08:15.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right! Let's finish them!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.55,0:08:21.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Get ready!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.52,0:08:23.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Usopp!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.54,0:08:26.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hold these two!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.24,0:08:29.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna slice them up!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.79,0:08:33.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please hurry up... O-Or I'm gonna...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.58,0:08:36.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It won't take long!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.03,0:08:44.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Hey, what happened, Roro?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.03,0:08:47.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sharks!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.45,0:08:51.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why are sharks in a lake?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.64,0:08:53.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fools!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.09,0:08:55.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's technically a sea.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.68,0:09:00.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The fight between Akainu and Aokiji left \Na crater just like after an explosion.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.55,0:09:06.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And then seawater streamed in from \Na big crack and created a lake.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.20,0:09:13.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course, so did a lot of sea life.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.83,0:09:15.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Zoro!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.60,0:09:22.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sharks! Scary! Sharks! Zoro \Ngot bitten by a shark!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.20,0:09:25.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Aim carefully! There is \Nnothing they can do now!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.47,0:09:28.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We have no place to go!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.48,0:09:30.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Blow them to kingdom come!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.64,0:09:38.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?! I've never thought \Nmy life would end like this!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.62,0:09:44.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is it!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.99,0:09:49.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fire!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.58,0:09:54.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.63,0:09:59.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What? What happened?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.56,0:10:05.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Brook!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.13,0:10:11.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is colder than a freezing blizzard?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.51,0:10:15.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's the wind from the underworld.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.32,0:10:21.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You bastard!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.51,0:10:28.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, did I mention I froze your gun barrels?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.62,0:10:31.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So they'll explode if you shoot!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.34,0:10:35.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who are you, skull mask?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.06,0:10:38.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My name is not worth mentioning. It's Brook.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.51,0:10:40.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You just mentioned it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.21,0:10:44.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm a skeleton who came back from \Nthe dead and put my second life...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.98,0:10:50.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...in the hands of the Straw Hat captain!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.27,0:10:54.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,People call me Soul King!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.05,0:10:57.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When did he freeze our guns?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.72,0:10:59.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's unforgivable!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.23,0:11:05.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Unforgivable"? Right back at you!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.57,0:11:09.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--You bastard!\N--How dare you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.95,0:11:14.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Losing friends - I'm sick of it (korigori)!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.02,0:11:14.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.46,0:11:19.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And it sounds like ice (koori)!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.62,0:11:23.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's fast! He sure can fight!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.50,0:11:25.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't know they had another crewmember!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.95,0:11:28.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But it doesn't matter now!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.66,0:11:33.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Because they already became shark food.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.47,0:11:39.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,See for yourself!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.70,0:11:42.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The sharks got their butts kicked!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.11,0:11:49.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, where did they go?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.68,0:11:52.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're here!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.49,0:11:56.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're just in time, Brook.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.93,0:11:59.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm glad that you're okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.08,0:12:04.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was chased by a strange thing \Nand happened to come this far.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.84,0:12:09.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nice try, you part-human-part-animals!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.21,0:12:12.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But sharks can't stop us!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.58,0:12:19.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're way stronger than that!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.23,0:12:22.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But no matter... how strong we are...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.49,0:12:24.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,we can't stand the cold!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.51,0:12:27.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's freezing! I'm gonna turn to ice!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.24,0:12:29.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"I TOLD YOU GUYS..." I rold you guys...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.56,0:12:29.54,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,"WE CAN'T JUST GO TO THE \NCOLD SIDE LIKE THIS...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.56,0:12:33.53,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,We can't hust go to the \Ncold shide like this...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.55,0:12:38.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But look. We're lucky.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.23,0:12:42.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We should be glad that we ran into them.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.21,0:12:46.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Boss, they're right on top of us!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.38,0:12:50.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait! They look familiar!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.17,0:12:52.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He looks good!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.28,0:12:55.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll take the fourth guy from the right.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.85,0:12:57.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.31,0:13:00.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll take the guy next to him.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.31,0:13:01.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll take that one.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.89,0:13:06.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The girl at the far left.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.31,0:13:14.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are they talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.48,0:13:17.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Their clothes look warm!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.82,0:13:17.80,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,"ALL RIGHT... PLEASE GET ME ONE, TOO!"
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.82,0:13:22.91,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,All right... flease ket me one, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.93,0:13:26.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are they looking to rip our coats off?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.43,0:13:31.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're terrible! Do they wanna rob us?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.60,0:13:39.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know! That hat!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.10,0:13:43.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He is the rookie of that worst \Ngeneration from two years ago!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.68,0:13:44.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.92,0:13:46.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.78,0:13:49.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He is Fire Fist's brother!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.15,0:13:51.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whaaat?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.03,0:13:57.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A pirate with a 400 million \Nberry bounty - Straw Hat Luffy!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.24,0:14:03.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,4... 400 million?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.46,0:14:07.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mil Fleurs!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.21,0:14:11.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What is that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.06,0:14:15.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No!!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.08,0:14:21.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Give me your clothes!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.21,0:14:24.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You'd better not fight back!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.85,0:14:30.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then I won't have to hurt you so bad!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.89,0:14:38.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, my friends. You're in \Nbetter shape than I thought!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.08,0:14:51.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Help me!!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.82,0:15:13.82,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,THE LABORATORY - IN FRONT \NOF THE MAIN ENTRANCE
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.63,0:15:25.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I told you, Smo-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.31,0:15:28.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is why I said I didn't \Nwant anything to do with him!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.25,0:15:36.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What should we do?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.24,0:15:52.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry up! Hi-ya! It's this way, kids!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.67,0:15:54.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We gotta find a backdoor!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.37,0:15:55.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.82,0:16:00.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go back! It was that man who cut me up!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.28,0:16:02.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What? Really?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.32,0:16:05.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then he may have the rest of your body?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.40,0:16:08.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, I don't think so!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.51,0:16:10.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then, it can wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.30,0:16:13.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait a minute! Maybe I can get a clue!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.79,0:16:15.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We have to find a backdoor!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.94,0:16:23.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We can't go back to face the Navy again!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.24,0:16:29.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't see any exit! Where is the backdoor?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.58,0:16:37.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right! Super count on me!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.02,0:16:41.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You got some kind of sensor on you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.06,0:16:42.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no such a thing!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.62,0:16:50.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then why did you take the lead?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.16,0:16:51.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That was that samurai...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.71,0:16:54.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go! Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.68,0:16:57.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...And the Straw Hats.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.34,0:16:59.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't let them escape!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.71,0:17:05.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Room!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.06,0:17:13.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is this?! It's like a thin film...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.05,0:17:22.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shambles!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.50,0:17:36.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What was that? I felt something weird!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.83,0:17:39.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No time to think about it now!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.23,0:17:42.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Alright, keep running, brats!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.50,0:17:46.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh? Did I drop my cigarette?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.99,0:17:49.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Follow me!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.80,0:17:51.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.75,0:17:55.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, this is no time for you \Nto fool around, Sanji-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.23,0:17:58.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In this week's episode, I'm super!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.84,0:18:03.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll find a backdoor in a moment!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.28,0:18:04.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.80,0:18:07.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Everybody?\N--There's something wrong with you!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.53,0:18:10.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.15,0:18:18.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come to think of it, my \Nbreasts feel lighter...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.74,0:18:23.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What happened?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.86,0:18:27.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,These are...! I got big breasts!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.26,0:18:30.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I-I turned into a human!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.49,0:18:35.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When did it happen? I'm a racoon now?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.35,0:18:38.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,E-Everybody, calm down!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.80,0:18:41.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's do a roll call!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.06,0:18:42.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Chopper!\N--Here!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.76,0:18:45.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Franky!\N--Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.36,0:18:47.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sanji-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.02,0:18:49.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.68,0:18:51.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nami-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.54,0:18:53.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're Nami... aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.83,0:18:56.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh-huh!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.29,0:19:04.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is going on here?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.14,0:19:11.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Law, you bastard!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.91,0:19:13.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you want?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.00,0:19:16.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Give us back our ship.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.38,0:19:17.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.56,0:19:18.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Really?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.87,0:19:26.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But you can't have it as it is now.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.67,0:19:48.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--It's falling toward us!\N--Run!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.97,0:20:09.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's retreat for now, Vice \NAdmiral! His power is too creepy!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.32,0:20:11.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We can't fight him!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.52,0:20:19.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't let anyone leave!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.09,0:20:27.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's been fused to the rocks of the island?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.86,0:20:30.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He made some sort of strange \Nartwork with the ship!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.30,0:20:36.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn! We can't make it back \Nto the base without the ship!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.70,0:20:39.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Warlords work for the Government!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.06,0:20:42.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're breaking your \Ncontract by attacking us!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.69,0:20:44.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Trafalgar!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.11,0:20:48.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--We'll report this to headquarters!\N--They'll strip you of your title!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.87,0:20:52.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry about me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.12,0:20:54.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Scan!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.45,0:21:01.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's this?! Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.37,0:21:03.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Transponder Snails?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.72,0:21:05.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh? Mine's gone!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.35,0:21:07.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No way... So is mine!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.42,0:21:10.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Those are ours!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.06,0:21:12.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He took all of our Transponder Snails!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.62,0:21:15.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't let you tell the \Nheadquarters or the Government
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.94,0:21:23.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,about anything that you've \Nseen on this island.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.63,0:21:31.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You stupid pirate, don't push your luck!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.53,0:21:35.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Smo-yan!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.66,0:21:42.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You ate the Op-Op Fruit and you're \Nthe Modification Man, I believe!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.81,0:21:48.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stay out of his sword's reach!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.55,0:21:52.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I got cut!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.22,0:21:55.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? But I'm alive!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.69,0:21:58.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You guys are in my way! \NGet out of the circle!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.26,0:22:00.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The circle?!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.15,0:22:02.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,While you're in the circle he created,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.56,0:22:05.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,you're like a patient on an operating table!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.84,0:22:07.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is his operating room.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.59,0:22:11.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He has total control over it and can \Nmanipulate anything as he pleases!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.40,0:22:16.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's the Surgeon of Death!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.24,0:22:18.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Trafalgar!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.46,0:22:20.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you really wanna do this...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.39,0:22:22.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't do it, Tashigi!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.09,0:22:30.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your Haki is not strong enough!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.19,0:23:01.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Captain-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.54,0:23:09.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,With Tashigi being cut down,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.96,0:23:14.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the thugs of the Navy's G-5 unit were \Nalso about to face annihilation.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.09,0:23:17.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But then Smoker faces Law.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.14,0:23:20.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A duel between a Warlord and a \NNavy Vice-Admiral finally begins.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.72,0:23:24.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Their fierce battle that destroys \Neverything around them
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.18,0:23:26.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,suddenly takes an unexpected turn.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.81,0:23:28.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,On the next episode of One Piece!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.11,0:23:30.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Meeting Again After Two Years!\NLuffy and Law!"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.71,0:23:38.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna be King of the Pirates!!
